title: Browns-Bengals TNF Recap: Baker Mayfield and Joe Burrow both impress (Football 9/18)
description:
The Browns are on the board! Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Josh Edwards break down Cleveland's 35-30 victory over the Bengals on Thursday Night Football. This game featured two #1 overall picks at the quarterback position and both delivered. Which QB was the bigger takeaway? Joe Burrow threw over 60 passes in just his second career game while Baker Mayfield improved mightily from his Week 1 performance. The guys break down all you need to know from TNF.
